01:03:21,210 --> 01:03:22,580
Was I a burden to you…

1093
01:03:22,670 --> 01:03:24,210
because I'm unwell?

1094
01:03:24,290 --> 01:03:25,880
So get up.

1095
01:03:25,960 --> 01:03:27,840
Get up and walk!

1096
01:03:27,920 --> 01:03:30,630
I also really want to know

1097
01:03:30,720 --> 01:03:32,930
why I was abandoned.

1098
01:03:33,010 --> 01:03:35,220
Mom, Dad is here.

1099
01:03:35,300 --> 01:03:37,770
Mi-joo, let's get married.

1100
01:03:37,850 --> 01:03:40,270
I'm going to marry Kang-ho oppa.

1101
01:03:40,350 --> 01:03:42,940
-Okay?
-Are you home?

1102
01:03:43,020 --> 01:03:46,860
Please keep my illness
a secret from the villagers.

1103
01:03:47,360 --> 01:03:49,190
It's here. The evidence.

1104
01:03:49,280 --> 01:03:50,490
To my mother whom I miss dearly.

1105
01:03:50,570 --> 01:03:52,700
Are you healthy and well?

